videos.headline: Utah's Moss takes it 58 yards for TD
videos.description: Zack Moss runs right through the heart of the West Virginia defense for 58 yards to get the Utes on the board in the Heart of Dallas Bowl.

videos.headline: Utah's punter throws interception
videos.description: West Virginia's Shane Commodore is the lucky recipient of a Mitch Wishnowsky interception on a botched punt.

videos.headline: Moss runs wild as Utah tops West Virginia
videos.description: Utah's Zack Moss rushes for 150 yards and a touchdown in a 30-14 victory against West Virginia in the Zaxby's Heart of Dallas Bowl. With the win, Utes head coach Kyle Whittingham improves to 11-1 in bowl games.
